name: TBRNewsMediaFlashBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des: TBR News Media Flash Briefing brings you the latest news about Long Island, NY — headlines about politics, business, crime, events and the stories that affect your life every day. Want to know more? Listen now and read the latest at TBRNewsMedia.com Add TBR News Media to your Flash Briefing and move it to the top of your news by going to Settings in the Alexa app. You can manage your Flash Briefing under Account.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
